$DEF_BOITE
Gosub HORODAT From WGFBOMROU
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Inpbox "FBOMROU" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [BOWH]
&   Folder Mask [BOW1]
& , Folder Mask [BOW2]
& , Folder Mask [BOW4]
& As [BOW1]
Titled [BOW1] TIT
Return

$VISU_BOITE
Gosub INIT_BOITE
Gosub HORODAT From WGFBOMROU
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Inpbox "FBOMROU" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [BOWH]
&   Folder Mask [BOW1]
& , Folder Mask [BOW2]
& , Folder Mask [BOW4]
& As [BOW1]
Titled [BOW1] TIT
Gosub AFF_BOITE
Return

$AFF_BOITE
